	<LINE>period of five years, the insured person shall be</LINE>
	<LINE>unable to continue, or shall desire to discontinue,</LINE>
	<LINE>such payments, a portion of tlie premiums paid by</LINE>
	<LINE>him, which portion will in no case be less than</LINE>
	<LINE>one-third of the whole sum paid by him, will be</LINE>
	<LINE>returned to him.</LINE>
