	<LINE>A woman of the same age can pur-</LINE>
	<LINE>chase a like annuity for . . 84 19 2</LINE>
	<LINE>The sums to be charged for the purchase of</LINE>
	<LINE>deferred annuities or deferred monthly allow-</LINE>
	<LINE>ances will vary with the age and sex of the person</LINE>
	<LINE>on whose life the annuity or monthly allowance</LINE>
